show.description: Flora ka heartbreak usse le aata hai Vito Morelli ke paas.Ek vampire jiska past uski shakal se juda hai. Jab love, revenge aur supernatural secrets takraate hain, toh hota hai ek aisa romance jo dil bhi todta hai aur jaan bhi leta hai. Dekhiye “Dracula’s Kiss”  jahan ek kiss sab kuch badal deta hai.
